data.description: This townhome, with immense curb appeal, has been recently repainted, reroofed and has had updated siding. Tastefully refreshed interior with three bedrooms on the upper level and a beautiful, lower-level bedroom and bathroom . A walk out patio with a small, fenced space is perfect for backyard BBQs and pets. Plenty of complex parking with a tight-knit-neighborly feel. Realize your dreams of being in the center of the vibrant Carbondale community or owning a profitable rental in a location with robust rental rates.
